graph TB
    subgraph "Model Registry Operator"
        Controller[model-registry-operator<br/>Controller]
        Webhook[Webhook Server<br/>Port 9443]
        Controller -->|validates/defaults| Webhook
    end

    subgraph "Model Registry Instance"
        RestAPI[model-registry REST service<br/>Port 8080]
        RBACProxy[kube-rbac-proxy<br/>Sidecar Port 8443]
        Catalog[Model Catalog<br/>Optional]

        RBACProxy -->|forwards after authz| RestAPI
    end

    subgraph "Data Storage"
        PostgreSQL[PostgreSQL DB<br/>Port 5432]
        MySQL[MySQL DB<br/>Port 3306]
    end

    User[User/Client] -->|creates| ModelRegistryCR[ModelRegistry CR<br/>v1beta1]
    ModelRegistryCR -->|watched by| Controller

    Controller -->|creates| Deployment[Deployment<br/>REST API + Proxy]
    Controller -->|creates| Service[Service<br/>8443/8080]
    Controller -->|creates| Route[OpenShift Route<br/>HTTPS]
    Controller -->|creates| DBResources[DB Resources<br/>PVC/Deployment/Service]
    Controller -->|creates| NetworkPolicy[NetworkPolicy<br/>DB Isolation]

    Deployment -->|contains| RestAPI
    Deployment -->|contains| RBACProxy

    RestAPI -->|persists metadata| PostgreSQL
    RestAPI -.->|alternative| MySQL

    Controller -->|integrates| Platform[components.platform.opendatahub.io]
    Controller -->|watches| AuthServices[services.platform.opendatahub.io/auths]

    RBACProxy -->|validates token| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API<br/>SubjectAccessReview]

    Route -->|exposes| Service
    Service -->|routes to| RBACProxy

    style Controller fill:#4a90e2
    style Webhook fill:#4a90e2
    style RestAPI fill:#7ed321
    style RBACProxy fill:#f5a623
    style PostgreSQL fill:#e8e8e8
    style MySQL fill:#e8e8e8
    style ModelRegistryCR fill:#f5a623
    style Platform fill:#7ed321
    style AuthServices fill:#7ed321
    style Catalog fill:#7ed321
